{
  "stem": "15694.6",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "Now usually the 50 being killed come from the group where the person worked, but we knew he would not take anybody from the garage.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "So this fellow came from Bochnia, but we actually came from the ammunition camp of Klaj, spelled Kel-- K-L-A-J.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "So we hoped that the connection between Bochnia wouldn't been-- us and Bochnia wouldn't have been known.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "Anyway, 50 were taken to the killing hill at that time.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "That was before the incident when he shot at me.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "And also out of the 50-- it was late in the evening.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "They were going to be-- they were killed that night, but they were not sort of buried yet.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "And during the night, one of them also managed to get up.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "He was wounded.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "And he came-- and they had to undress, so they came naked into the neighboring workshop.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "And of course, they gave him-- they helped him.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "So I'm not the only one.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "It must have happened-- things might-- that way must've happened more than once.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "Now that was another incident.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "Now I switch back to the point of escape where I had to tell my father something terrible has happened.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "The point where we want to escape has now been-- sort of another coil of wire has been placed in front of it.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "So we have to make another plan, my father said.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "Now further in this camp-- and I'm not speaking now in sequence because that's the way that my memory goes.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "I'm sorry.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Further in this camp, once we were all called out-- alles raus auf den Appellplatz-- to go to the assembly place.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We were wondering what is it about-- anymore shootings or anything.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We were always apprehensive.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But you well sort of stood there in rows of five.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
